# {{context|legal|lang=en}} The human [[genitalia]]; ''specifically'', the [[penis]].
#* '''1824''', {{w|Vagrancy Act 1824}} ([http://www.legislation.gov.uk/ukpga/1824/83/pdfs/ukpga_18240083_en.pdf 5 Geo. 4. c.&nbsp;83], United Kingdom), section 4:
